OL,7,FThe government "misunderstood and
OL,8,Fmisapplied" planning rules when it
OL,9,Fblocked Marks & Spencer's plans to
OL,10,Fdemolish one of its flagship London
OL,11,Fstores, the High Court has heard.
OL,13,FM&S wants to flatten and rebuild its
OL,14,Fstore in Oxford Street, claiming the
OL,15,Fredevelopment is "of fundamental
OL,16,Fimportance" to the future of London's
OL,17,FWest End.
