OL,5,CCourt told
OL,7,FThe plans were blocked by Levelling Up
OL,8,FSecretary Michael Gove last summer,
OL,9,Fwho said the building should be
OL,10,Frefurbished rather than demolished and
OL,11,Fthat demolition would negatively
OL,12,Fimpact nearby heritage assets,
OL,13,Fincluding the Grade II* listed
OL,14,FSelfridges store directly opposite.
