OL,5,CCourt told
OL,7,FThe company has brought legal action
OL,8,Fagainst the government, Westminster
OL,9,FCity Council and Save Britain's
OL,10,FHeritage over the decision, with its
OL,11,Flawyers telling a hearing in London on
OL,12,FTuesday that Mr Gove's "unusual"
OL,13,Fdecision should be quashed.
OL,15,FThe government and Save Britain's
OL,16,FHeritage are resisting the challenge,
OL,17,Fclaiming Mr Gove was entitled to make
OL,18,Fthe decision he did.
