OL,7,FM&S applied to the council in the
OL,8,Fsummer of 2021 for permission to
OL,9,Fdemolish Orchard House, its store in
OL,10,FOxford Street, and replace it with a
OL,11,Fnine-storey building that would
OL,12,Finclude retail space, a cafe, a gym
OL,13,Fand an office.
