OL,7,FMr Gove said in June 2022 that he
OL,8,Fwould decide on the application rather
OL,9,Fthan the council, which supported the
OL,10,Fplans along with the Greater London
OL,11,FAuthority.
OL,13,FBut he refused planning permission in
OL,14,FJuly 2023, overruling a government
OL,15,Fplanning inspector who gave his
OL,16,Fapproval to the plans in February last
OL,17,Fyear.
