OL,5,CCourt told
OL,7,FBut while Mr Gove acknowledged it was
OL,8,Funclear if there was "a viable and
OL,9,Fdeliverable alternative" to
OL,10,Fdemolition, there was no "compelling
OL,11,Fjustification" for it.
OL,13,FIn written arguments, Paul Shadarevian
OL,14,FKC, representing the Department for
OL,15,FLevelling Up, Housing and Communities,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The Secretary of State was
OL,17,Fentitled to say that in the
OL,18,Fcircumstances of this case, there
OL,19,Fshould be a strong presumption in
OL,20,Ffavour of reusing buildings."
