OL,7,FHe also said that if demolition was
OL,8,Fnot permitted, the extent of the
OL,9,Fnecessary refurbishment could create
OL,10,Fthe same or higher carbon emissions,
OL,11,Ftelling the court on Tuesday that the
OL,12,Fstore "would close" if left in its
OL,13,Fcurrent form due to it "significantly
OL,14,Fundertrading".
