OL,5,CCourt told
OL,7,FThe barrister told the court: "There
OL,8,Fis nothing more here than a general
OL,9,Fpositive encouragement of the
OL,10,Fconversion of existing buildings,
OL,11,Fwhich itself is entirely different
OL,12,Ffrom the wholesale, deep refurbishment
OL,13,Fwhich is at issue in this case."
OL,15,FHe added: "It has nothing that could
OL,16,Fbe described as a presumption, let
OL,17,Falone a strong presumption."
OL,19,FThe hearing before Mrs Justice Lieven
OL,20,Fis due to conclude on Wednesday, with
OL,21,Fa judgment expected at a later date.
